          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我在此做买卖的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众公子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，这是雁飞不到处，人为名利牵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位贵乡何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众公子分用各自本地语答。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们这样装扮，往哪里去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众公子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "都往彩楼，抢夺绣球，好招驸马。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，看他们这般嘴脸，未必公主还看得他上哎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位，我可去得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众公子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不论本国外国之人，都是去得的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "既然去得，你我一路同行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎哎哎，你们都不用去，这个驸马，是我定了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众公子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎见得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我衣才、貌才、人才、文才，四才全了，这驸马不是我还有谁？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众公子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎，姻缘大事，不可强求，少时便知。一同前往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "观他们似夜叉牛头马面，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贪新婚也去到彩楼台前。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛强、众公子同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎、哎、哎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子甲",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "论才貌我是个头名状元。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳、咳、咳，驸马爷来了，让开道。哈、哈、哈。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公子甲下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "四宫女→薛强",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
