    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众公子",
        "侍卫甲",
        "公子甲",
        "四侍卫",
        "四宫女",
        "孟九环",
        "薛强"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四御林军、四侍卫、四太监、四宫女引孟九环同上。〖牌子〗。孟九环上楼，四宫女同站楼上，四太监分"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "站两边板凳，四御林军、四侍卫同台下一字站。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宫娥，摆开香案！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四宫女",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。宫女摆桌。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "神圣在上，孟九环今日抛球招赘，以定终身。但愿绣球落于有缘之人也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "御香飘绕霞光现，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "（月中老人、四云童、四云旗同上，月中老人站孟九环背后椅子，四云童分站两边，四云旗分站四角四椅子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "薛强、众公子自两边分上，众公子同闲话。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祝告上苍含笑颜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "高结彩楼配良缘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休负牛女古渡边。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "百岁和谐咫尺间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鸾凤相引并头莲。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孟九环抬桌，下台。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四侍卫",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，你等不要罗咤，接着彩球者，即招驸马。站定了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众公子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众公子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。孟九环抛球，薛强接。众公子同拥薛强，薛强笑，众公子同闲话，四侍卫赶众公子同下，薛强"
        },
        {
          "character": "众公子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四宫女",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恭喜贵人：彩球中了一美貌少年。请公主启奏大王，择日婚配。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "摆驾！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。四宫女、四太监、孟九环同下台。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四宫女",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起驾！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同下。薛强捧彩球上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李药师真个是仙目如电，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天相助接彩球得配良缘。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众公子同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，你是个中原人怎么招得驸马？快快与我走开，让我好去成亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，这绣球落在我手，此乃天赐姻缘，谁敢争夺？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众公子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们要抢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谁敢来抢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "众公子",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我就抢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛强打众公子，众公子同下。侍卫甲上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "侍卫甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，那壮士不用打，此乃天缘相助。随到馆驿，将家乡名姓，写一庚帖，待宫"
        },
        {
          "character": "侍卫甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "女呈奏大王。随我来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水底鱼〗。薛强、侍卫甲同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
