    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "大太监甲",
        "孟九环",
        "孟方",
        "林光碧",
        "薛强"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四小太监、二大太监、孟方同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "玉镜人间传和璧，银河天上渡双星。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "北斗挂城边，南山倚殿前。龙凤金阙地，风绕戴尧天。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤，孟方，威镇大宛国为君。所生一女，乳名九环。高搭彩楼，招赘佳婿。还"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未交旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四宫女 （内同白） 公主朝参。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主朝参。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宣上金殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公主上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖小吹打〗。孟九环上，四宫女同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "莺歌闻太液，风吹绕瀛州。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿九环见驾，愿父王千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赐坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，彩球落在谁人之手？可问姓名？他容貌如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "父王吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "羞得我低下头不敢明讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽择婿还有那父母在堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟九环",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "观庚帖自有了梁鸿孟光。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孟九环下，四宫女同随下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，他乃大唐薛仁贵之孙，名曰薛强。哈哈，真乃女儿之福也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内侍，请薛爵主上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "薛爵主上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛强上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传来纶音飞鹦鹉，乐奏箫笙引凤凰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小将薛强见驾，愿国主千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爵主平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四爵主不在长安，因甚至此？"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因三哥薛刚，大闹花灯，踢死殿下，惊动朝廷。我蒙仙人相救，到此误闯彩"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "楼之下。国主恕罪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真乃千里姻缘一线牵。已遂小女之愿也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小将不敢玷辱金枝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃天配良缘，何必推辞？今日吉日良辰，就在金殿拜完花烛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，既不嫌弃，父王请上，儿臣拜过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内侍，请驸马后宫更衣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢父王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛强",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喜作乘鸾客，本为跨凤人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛强下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宣鸿胪寺上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "大太监甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鸿胪寺上殿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林光碧",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林光碧上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林光碧",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "百年琴瑟好，千载凤麟祥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林光碧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣林光碧见驾，愿大王千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林光碧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千千岁。宣微臣上殿，有何国事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今与公主完婚，好好赞礼上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林光碧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。伏以："
        },
        {
          "character": "林光碧",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "百尺红丝千里牵，婚姻好合是前缘。天南地北成佳偶，始信安居两周全。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林光碧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请新贵人台升。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四宫女扶薛强、孟九环自两边分上，同拜堂。上半段尾声。四宫女、薛强、孟九环同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟方",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且喜女儿终身有托，孤王才得放心。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（下半段尾声。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
